<l>aritarō tēṟṟa maṟivuṭaiyār kaṇṇum </l>
<l>pirivō riṭattuṇmai yāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As even the lover who understands (everything) may at times depart, confidence is hardly possible.</l>
